citeinfo.title: UO_GIS_EDIT.UOMGR.Buildings

descript.abstract: This file displays the location and shape of the buildings at the University of Oregon campus- Eugene, Oregon. This dataset is stored is an AcrSDE feature class in SQL.
descript.purpose: Dataset was produced for the purpose of planning, mapping and facilities maintenance of the University of Oregon
descript.supplinf: This dataset is stored in the InfoGraphics Campus Geodatabase - housed in 163 Condon. Building polygons were created by digitizing rooflines from 2002 digital orthophotos. Polygons were then referneced with CAD bookplan drawings to obtain footprints. Polygons were then referenced with building footprint data produced by photrogrammetry at Spencer B Gross (October 2003) to verify positional accuracy.
